{"tid":837342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣西新傳媒中心一柱擎天 射煙花慶中秋","createTime":"2018-09-26T09:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:27:21.000Z","uid":3560,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"adcc549dd36fc9ab91a45fa1f967b0bb59ba3999","tid":837342,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=feZkBT_A-ec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfeZkBT_A-ec&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e8fe60cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=feZkBT_A-ec</a><br />\n<br />\n中國大國崛起的氣魄，已體現在國內的建築風格上。位於廣西南寧的廣西新媒體中心，因為其「一柱擎天」的獨特造型，而引來網民熱議。近日更有人悉心製作惡搞影片，令大廈頂端射出一道道煙花，成功引起外媒關注，令新建築「揚名國際」。<br />\n<br />\n這座廣西新媒體中心在2016年8月動工，如今工程已進入尾聲。南寧市委機關報《南寧日報》在今年6月介紹過這座建築，指項目預算總投資約19.66億元人民幣，總建築面積25.7萬平方米。當時報道形容大廈「宛如綿延的梯田，具有壯鄉山水畫的美感」，三座主體結構「已展雄姿」進入最後裝飾階段。<br />\n<br />\n不過眼利的網民一看就發現，所謂如「綿延梯田」的新媒體中心，看起來明明就像男性生殖器。近日網上更流出一段15秒的影片，顯示建築物在晚上綻放耀眼光芒，頂端射出一道道煙花，氣魄非凡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/erect-03_4jsUL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ferect-03_4jsUL_1200x0.png&h=d2d6ba54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片隨即在網上廣傳。不過大陸梨視頻引述廣西廣電網路有限公司的工作人員稱，這段煙花影片只是網民惡搞。工作人員稱建築尚未修築完成，根本不能放煙花。至於建築物的「獨特」外型，工作人員就指是拍攝角度的問題，若正面看應該會見到山的形狀。<br />\n<br />\n不論煙花片段是真是假，這個獨特的建築已經成為國際笑話。英國《每日郵報》、《太陽報》、《鏡報》等，均紛紛轉載這段「陽具煙花」片段，部分報道寫得非常直白，形容煙花就如一道又一道的精液。<br />\n<br />\n影片亦在大陸微博引來熱議。不少大陸網民更將新媒体中心與廣西體育中心相提並論，認為兩者可謂是互相輝映。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E5%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%88-%E4%B8%80%E6%9F%B1%E6%93%8E%E5%A4%A9-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%83%A1%E6%90%9E%E7%85%99%E8%8A%B1%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E5%82%B3%E9%81%8D%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25BB%2588-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%259F%25B1%25E6%2593%258E%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%2590%259E%25E7%2585%2599%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%2581%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=66fcdba1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25BB%2588-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%259F%25B1%25E6%2593%258E%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%2590%259E%25E7%2585%2599%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%2581%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F&h=8655a35c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E5%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%88-%E4%B8%80%E6%9F%B1%E6%93%8E%E5%A4%A9-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%83%A1%E6%90%9E%E7%85%99%E8%8A%B1%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E5%82%B3%E9%81%8D%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/</a>"},{"pid":"1d0a0e23e28c9336cb5cbf158eb87d9eef4c39eb","tid":837342,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0effe5d57a9000a839c58b61b8f2b459bcb46053","tid":837342,"uid":144626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"南寧真係慘，畀人滅族又畀d北佬搞傳銷搞臭個朵，而家又整棟射精樓<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知個城點解咁黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae8f383293f3a0d1e1e2af6fc29dcc239bc19a4","tid":837342,"uid":3560,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.600496.com/upload/images/20171230/1514601789136376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.600496.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F20171230%2F1514601789136376.jpg&h=4c4acd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔離仲有個閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"